          "id": "9bd04e7103eda50482452d9a1d8d6c932fb24380",
          "message": "Split up the typechecker into a module with multiple files\n\n- Extract the typed AST (TCType, SExprTE & friends, Typed{List,Map,Struct}Expr,\n  TypedDsrvSpecification, Display impls) into lang/dsrv/typed_ast.rs,\n  mirroring the untyped ast.rs\n- Split the checker into type_checker/{expr,strict,gradual,types}.rs:\n  the shared expression-level checking machinery, the strict driver,\n  the gradual fixed-point inference driver, and errors/traits/value\n  validation respectively, each with its tests inline\n- Move PartialStreamValue and its Value conversions to core/values.rs,\n  fixing the inverted core -> lang::dsrv::type_checker dependency from\n  stream_casting.rs\n- Delete the unused TypedDataList\n- Re-export everything from type_checker/mod.rs so existing import\n  paths keep working\n- Move the proptest regression file to match the proptest's new\n  source location",
